T*
(arguments compiles the full program and produces the executable analyzer. The required build) Tj
T*
( command is:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(make) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(If the executable or object files from an earlier build should be removed first, the ) Tj
T*
(repository also provides the command:) Tj
T*
() Tj
