(## 5.3 Architecture Diagram) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The diagram below shows the three concurrently running worker processes and the two ) Tj
T*
(dedicated pipes that connect each worker to the controller. The controller creates and ) Tj
T*
(connects these pipes in spawn_worker\(\) at controller.c:182. The controller holds the write ) Tj
T*
(end of each task pipe and the read end of each result pipe; each worker holds the ) Tj
T*
(complementary ends. All other pipe ends are closed immediately after forking inside ) Tj
T*
(spawn_worker\(\) at controller.c:182.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
