T*
(that type is MSG_TASK, and then analyzes the named file. The filename must fit within the ) Tj
T*
(fixed-size filename buffer; if it does not, the controller marks the task as failed locally ) Tj
T*
(instead of sending a malformed message. After a valid MSG_TASK is received, the worker must ) Tj
