T*
(dispatch_task_to_worker\(\) at controller.c:292, the controller treats that worker as dead ) Tj
T*
(through handle_worker_failure\(\) at controller.c:262, closes the pipe endpoints associated ) Tj
T*
(with it, and re-queues the unfinished task so that another live worker can process it later.) Tj
T*
